data.description: Stylish Two Story with Pool in Canterberry South! Great curb appeal w/cozy front porch & stone accents. Front entry opens to formal dining room. Spacious kitchen features white cabinets, large center island w/quartz counters, pendant lights, stainless steel appliances & walk-in pantry. Dinette opens to low deck, above-ground pool w/deck & fully fenced backyard. Living room w/stone fireplace, wall of windows & ceiling fan. Drop zone just off the kitchen that leads to pantry. 2nd level showcases 4 bedrooms, loft space & large laundry room. Primary bedroom has ceiling fan, walk-in closet & 3/4 bath w/double sinks. Bedrooms 2, 3 & 4 have easy access to full hall bath. Loft is perfect for an office, reading nook &/or craft area. Lots of potential in the unfinished lower level w/rough-in & egress window. 3 car garage, backyard shed & convenient location as close to Hwy 6/31, schools & shopping. Home is move-in ready!
